<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.2.6">
<l>miṉṉa ṉaiya nuṇṇi ṭaiyār viriku ḻalmēl nuḻainta vaṇṭu</l>
<l>viṉṉi caikkum villi puttū riṉita marntā yuṉṉaik kaṇṭā</l>
<l>reṉṉa nōṉpu nōṟṟāḷ kolō vivaṉaip peṟṟa vayiṟu ṭaiyā</l>
<l>ḷeṉṉum vārttai yeytu vitta viruṭī kēcā mulaiyu ṇāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who see you who abides sweetly in Villiputtūr where bees</l>
<l>who crawl on the loose locks of ladies with lightning thin waists</l>
<l rend="indent">hum sweet [sounds]</l>
<l>ask ‘what penance has she with the womb that begot him endured?’</l>
<l>Hṛṣīkeśa, who causes [such] talk to occur, drink from [my] breast!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
